title: Hour 2 - Jerry Jones on Cooper Rush, Dan Orlovsky

description:
Dan talks to former NFL QB Dan Orlovsky drops by and talks about Miami Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa's injury saga. And DP weighs in on Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones' latest comments about QB Cooper Rush.
